# Week 2: Case Law Data Collection

**Filename:** `work/week2_case_collection.md`

**Objective:** Build comprehensive database of relevant judgments

**Time Allocated:** 18 hours

---

## Search Strategy

### India Kanoon Search Protocol

**Database:** https://indiankanoon.org

**Date Range:** 2020-01-01 to Present (focus on post-UPI implementation)

**Geographic Scope:** All High Courts (with focus on Kerala, Delhi, Bombay, Karnataka, Madras)

---

